title: Nokia 's net sales 1999 to 2019
summary: In general Net sales in billion euros has fallen over the Year.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2012 and 2013.
The highest Net sales in billion euros, of value 51.06 was reached at Year 2007
Minimum Net sales in billion euros about 11.76 was reached at Year 2014
